# =============================================================================
# finance-research-eval — ANTI-LEAK .gitignore (deny-by-default for anything
# that could expose the private/enterprise stack or real data).
#
# Rule of thumb: this PUBLIC repo ships ONLY the framework, schemas, gates,
# synthetic fixtures, mock connectors, and docs. If a path below could ever
# hold real data, secrets, or a real connector, it is excluded here.
# When in doubt, exclude. See OPEN-CORE.md for the boundary.
# =============================================================================

# --- Secrets & credentials (NEVER commit) -----------------------------------
*.env
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets/
**/secrets/
credentials*
*.credentials
.aws/
.netrc

# --- Real data (NEVER commit; only synthetic fixtures are versioned) --------
corpora/
data/
datasets/
runs/
out/
cache/
*.parquet
*.feather
# Benchmarks are downloaded by the user, never redistributed:
**/financebench/raw/
**/finqa/raw/
**/convfinqa/raw/
**/tatqa/raw/

# --- Enterprise / private boundary ------------------------------------------
# The enterprise edition lives in a SEPARATE private repo. If anyone ever
# clones it alongside this one, these paths must never be tracked here.
enterprise/
private/
connectors/real/
**/connectors/real/
scoring/proprietary/
**/proprietary/
compliance/operational/
marbo/

# --- Point-in-time / provider artifacts (paid sources, never public) --------
provider_*/
eodhd_*/
fmp_*/
tiingo_*/
sharadar_*/
point_in_time/

# --- Python -----------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
env/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# --- Node (if any tooling is added later) -----------------------------------
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# --- OS / editor ------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
*.log

# --- Build / dist -----------------------------------------------------------
build/
dist/
*.tar.gz
